# AgentSight Day 0 — AI Toolkit / | ai diagnostics (run as admin in Search)

| rest splunk_server=local /servicesNS/nobody/Splunk_ML_Toolkit/configs/conf-commands/ai
| eval check="ai_command_registered"
| table title disabled check

| rest splunk_server=local /servicesNS/nobody/Splunk_ML_Toolkit/storage/collections/data/mltk_ai_commander_collection count=0
| eval check="mltk_kv_collection"
| table title check

| rest splunk_server=local /services/server/info
| eval check="kvstore_status"
| table kvStoreStatus check

| rest splunk_server=local /services/apps/local
| search title="Splunk_ML_Toolkit" OR title="Splunk_SA_Scientific*"
| table title version disabled check

| makeresults count=1
| eval prompt="Classify this MCP agent behavior: 15 identical splunk_run_query calls in 10 minutes. Reply with classification, confidence, and reasoning."
| ai provider=Ollama model=llama3.2:latest connection=ollama_local prompt="'{prompt}'"
